700801f-c.title: Bronx: Cornell Avenue - Bolton Avenue
700801f-c.text:
Cornell Avenue, east of Bolton Avenue, showing the Monnot House.
It stood in the middle of Cornell Avenue. It was torn down
between 1923 and 1927.
Views 1,2:  1914
MAY BE REPRODUCED
View 3:  June 17, 1993
